Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Hmm... Will the envoy from Akdilek become a new member of the Gray Ravens?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Hassen', 3: "I'm not sure for how long, but it appears so.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Hassen', 3: "After all, it was a request from the Akdilek leader. It'd be impolite to refuse.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sophia', 3: "...I'm here on behalf of the Akdilek Commercial Alliance.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Hassen', 3: 'Sophia, you may be here as an envoy—', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Hassen', 3: "—But we'd like to welcome you to Babylonia as a comrade.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Celica', 3: "You don't have to be so formal, Hassen.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Celica', 3: 'After all, we transferred you to the Gray Ravens hoping that you can integrate with us by conducting joint operations.', 4: '1'}
